data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 4 bedroom, CORNER LOT craftsman home! Conveniently located just south of the city, this wonderfully maintained home boasts an abundance of daily natural light, filling its open floor plan and vast living room w/ fireplace. The large dining room space flows seamlessly into the kitchen, connected by hardwood flooring and tall ceilings. The spacious eat in kitchen is perfect for any at home chef with its big kitchen island, plentiful cabinet space, granite countertops, bar area, and walk in pantry. A floor plan perfect for entertaining guests, open up the doors to the fenced in back yard / patio and enjoy quiet evenings with loved ones! Upstairs, you'll first find the oversized primary bedroom suite - the perfect setting for maximum relaxation while also proving versatility for design and furnishings. The large walk in closet, double vanities, private water closet, and separate shower/soaking tub are the cherry on the top! Being one of a handful of 4 bedroom homes, take advantage of the 3 additional upstairs bedrooms - all of ample size and that are perfect as children's rooms, guest rooms, and/or an office. The 2 car garage and large attic space round out this lovely home! Set in the well known River Station neighborhood, amenities include a clubhouse, pool and playground! A short drive to the airport and downtown ATL, this home offers great space, a VERY convenient location, and being a back corner lot home, plenty of privacy to make it feel like home. Schedule your showing today!
